The July 2026 update for the Songstats API is here, and we added new Top Commenters endpoints, Apple Music ID lookup support, richer track and chart responses, and regional position data for Apple Music playlists.
We also made significant query-performance improvements across the Enterprise API, cutting latency and improving response times for almost all endpoints.
You can find the full list of API changes below.

New Additions
New Endpoints: /artists/top_commentors, /collaborators/top_commentors, /labels/top_commentors
Added Top Commenters data for artists, collaborators, and labels across YouTube and SoundCloud.
