Apple Music Lookup Support
Tracks and artists can now be requested directly using their Apple Music IDs. Use the new apple_music_track_id parameter across track endpoints and apple_music_artist_id across artist endpoints. Apple Music artist IDs can also be provided as the entity context for supported track requests.

Changes
Track and Chart Response Improvements
Track objects now include the is_remix field, making it easier to distinguish original releases from remixes.
When /tracks/info is requested with with_spotify_ids=true, artist objects now also include spotify_artist_id.

