The new only_current=true parameter on /tracks/stats can be used to exclude playlist and chart appearances that are no longer active.
{
"track_info": {
"songstats_track_id": "k4bp9etx",
"title": "Mr. Brightside",
"is_remix": true,
"artists": [
{
"name": "Don Diablo",
"songstats_artist_id": "48ra1cnv",
"spotify_artist_id": "28j8lBWDdDSHSSt5oPlsX2"
}
]
}
}
Regional Apple Music Playlist Positions
Regional Apple Music playlists returned by /tracks/stats now include separate position information for every available country.
The previous single playlist_country_code field has been replaced by is_regional and positions_by_country. Country codes are returned in uppercase, with current and historic position information for each market.
{
"source": "apple_music",
"data": {
"playlists": [
{
"applemusicid": "pl.example",
"name": "New Music Daily",
"top_position": 7,
"top_position_date": "2026-06-28",
"current_position": 12,
"added_at": "2026-06-20",
"removed_at": null,
"is_regional": true,
"positions_by_country": {
"US": {
"top_position": 7,
"top_position_date": "2026-06-28",
"current_position": 12,
"added_at": "2026-06-20T08:15:00.000Z",
"removed_at": null
},
